TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT Main.*, Sku_day.Exede_365Day FROM (SELECT item_id, cy_year_yyyy, cy_month_desc, as_of_date, facility_id, facility_name, inventory_type, uom, dollars, garments, Packages, stock_category, zstyle, inv_disposition_route, color_code, cup_size, size_code, size_desc, UPC_Code, historical_class_code, current_class_code, style_num, color_name, pack_code, garm_per_pkg_qty, inner_box_qty, sap_material_num, attribution_code, sku, sku_desc, sbu_desc, product_group_desc, Style_Group, category_desc, subcategory_desc, Brand_name, subbrand_desc, silhouette, selling_style, gender_desc, gender_category_desc, fabrication, oo_dollars, oo_garments, oo_Packages, lifecycle_desc, LIFESTYLE_DESC, PRODUCT_LINE_DESC, open_orders_Dollars_act, open_orders_Package_act, open_orders_Garments_act, Onhand_Dollars, Onhand_Package, Onhand_Garments, InTransit_Dollars, InTransit_Pakage, Intransit_Garments, put_up_cd FROM RPT_CLOSEOUT_COMP_LEVEL ) Main LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT endd, lifecycle_code, item_id, CASE WHEN ((SELECT AS_OF_DATE - 7 FROM DAY_DIMENSION WHERE (TRUNC(DAY_DATE) = TRUNC(SYSDATE)))- endd) >365 THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END AS Exede_365Day FROM (SELECT endd, lifecycle_code, item_id, dense_rank() over (partition BY Item_id order by endd DESC) AS rn FROM (SELECT MAX(end_date)endd, lifecycle_code, item_id FROM sku_lifecycle_class GROUP BY lifecycle_code, item_id ) ) WHERE rn = 2 )Sku_day ON Main.item_id =Sku_day.item_id

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT a.item_id, b.as_of_date, b.inventory_type, b.facility_id, c.inventory_src, b.from_facility_id, e.LEGACY_PUTUP_CODE as put_up_cd, b.stock_category, c.division_code, a.dollars, d.garm_per_pkg_qty, a.uom, d.style_num AS zstyle FROM inventory_adjustments a INNER JOIN inventory_exploded b ON (a.adjustment_id=b.adjustment_id) INNER JOIN (SELECT as_of_date-7 AS v_as_of_date FROM day_dimension WHERE day_date=TRUNC(sysdate) ) dd ON (b.as_of_date=dd.v_as_of_date) INNER JOIN bi_inventory c ON (b.parent_item_id =c.item_id AND b.as_of_date =c.as_of_date AND b.facility_id =c.facility_id AND b.from_facility_id=c.from_facility_id AND b.inventory_type =c.inventory_type) INNER JOIN stg_item_ora d ON (a.item_id=d.item_id) LEFT JOIN sap_item e on b.item_id = e.slba_item_id

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT a.item_id, a.as_of_date, a.inventory_type, a.facility_id, a.from_facility_id, x.LEGACY_PUTUP_CODE as put_up_cd, a.stock_category, b.division_code, a.dollars, a.garments, c.garm_per_pkg_qty, a.uom, d.style_num AS zstyle FROM inventory_exploded a LEFT OUTER JOIN bi_inventory b ON (a.parent_item_id = b.item_id AND a.facility_id = b.facility_id AND a.from_facility_id = b.from_facility_id AND a.inventory_type = b.inventory_type) INNER JOIN stg_item_ora c ON (a.item_id = c.item_id) INNER JOIN stg_item_ora d ON (a.parent_item_id = d.item_id) INNER JOIN (SELECT as_of_date-7 AS v_as_of_date FROM day_dimension WHERE day_date=TRUNC(sysdate) ) dd ON (a.as_of_date = dd.v_as_of_date AND b.as_of_date = dd.v_as_of_date) INNER JOIN sap_item x on a.item_id = x.slba_item_id WHERE b.legacy_lob NOT IN ('Intimates','Socks') UNION ALL SELECT a.item_id, a.as_of_date, a.inventory_type, a.facility_id, a.from_facility_id, x.LEGACY_PUTUP_CODE as put_up_cd, a.stock_category, 'SC' AS division_code, a.dollars, a.garments, c.garm_per_pkg_qty, a.uom, d.style_num AS zstyle FROM inventory_exploded a INNER JOIN stg_item_ora c ON (a.item_id = c.item_id) INNER JOIN stg_item_ora d ON (a.parent_item_id = d.item_id) INNER JOIN bi_inventory b ON (a.parent_item_id=b.item_id) INNER JOIN (SELECT as_of_date-7 AS v_as_of_date FROM day_dimension WHERE day_date=TRUNC(sysdate) ) dd ON (a.as_of_date = dd.v_as_of_date AND b.as_of_date = dd.v_as_of_date) LEFT JOIN sap_item x on a.item_id = x.slba_item_id WHERE b.legacy_lob = 'Socks'

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DAY_DIMENSION.AS_OF_DATE as AS_OF_DATE, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_MONTH_DESC as CY_MONTH_DESC, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_YEAR_YYYY as CY_YEAR_YYYY, DAY_DIMENSION.DAY_DATE as DAY_DATE FROM DAY_DIMENSION DAY_DIMENSION

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT itm_ora.attribution_code, itm_ora.division_group , itm_ora.sku , itm_ora.sku_desc, itm_ora.style_num, itm_ora.color_code, itm_ora.color_name, itm_ora.size_code, itm_ora.size_desc, itm_ora.cup_size, itm_ora.pack_code, itm_ora.upc_code, itm_ora.garm_per_pkg_qty, itm_ora.inner_box_qty, itm_ora.sap_material_num, itm_ora.historical_class_code , itm_ora.current_class_code, itm_ora.inv_disposition_route,
Inv_Table.item_id, Inv_Table.as_of_date, Inv_Table.inventory_type, Inv_Table.facility_id, Inv_Table.stock_category, Inv_Table.dollars, Inv_Table.garments, Inv_Table.uom, Inv_Table.zstyle, Inv_Table.put_up_cd,
OO_Table.oo_dollars, OO_Table.oo_garments, OO_Table.oo_packages,
sm1.brand_name, sm1.category_desc, sm1.fabrication, sm1.product_line_desc, sm1.silhouette, sm1.subbrand_desc, sm1.subcategory_desc, sm1.product_group_desc, sm1.gender_desc, sm1.gender_category_desc, sm1.lifestyle_desc, sm1.sbu_desc, sm1.style_group, sm1.selling_style,
f.facility_id, f.facility_name,
lc.lifecycle_desc,
CASE WHEN row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY DECODE(itm_ora.division_group,'SLS',itm_ora.sku,itm_ora.sku_desc) order by Inv_Table.zstyle nulls FIRST,f.facility_id ) =1 THEN -- SUM(NVL(OO_Table.oo_dollars,0)) NVL(OO_Table.oo_dollars,0) ELSE 0 END open_orders_dollars_act, CASE WHEN row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY DECODE(itm_ora.division_group,'SLS',itm_ora.sku,itm_ora.sku_desc) order by Inv_Table.zstyle nulls FIRST,f.facility_id ) =1 THEN -- SUM(NVL(OO_Table.oo_packages,0)) NVL(OO_Table.oo_packages,0) ELSE 0 END open_orders_packages_act, CASE WHEN row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY DECODE(itm_ora.division_group,'SLS',itm_ora.sku,itm_ora.sku_desc) order by Inv_Table.zstyle nulls FIRST,f.facility_id ) =1 THEN -- SUM(NVL(OO_Table.oo_garments,0)) NVL(OO_Table.oo_garments,0) ELSE 0 END open_orders_garments_act FROM stg_item_ora itm_ora INNER JOIN (SELECT item_id, as_of_date, inventory_type, facility_id, stock_category, dollars, garments, uom, zstyle, put_up_cd FROM STG_CLOSEOUT_INV_COMP UNION SELECT item_id, as_of_date, inventory_type, facility_id, stock_category, dollars, garments, uom, zstyle, put_up_cd FROM STG_CLOSEOUT_INV_ADJ_COMP ) Inv_Table ON itm_ora.item_id=Inv_Table.item_id LEFT OUTER JOIN STG_CLOSEOUT_COMP_OO OO_Table ON itm_ora.item_id=OO_Table.item_id LEFT OUTER JOIN style_master_1 sm1 ON itm_ora.style_num =sm1.style_num AND upper(itm_ora.division_group)=upper(sm1.division_group) AND itm_ora.company_code =sm1.company_code INNER JOIN slba_facility f ON Inv_Table.facility_id=f.facility_id AND f.facility_code <>'IDC' --AND f.facility_name NOT LIKE 'OM-%' LEFT OUTER JOIN lifecycle_class lc ON lc.lifecycle_code = DECODE(Inv_Table.stock_category,'ZOFQ','I', DECODE(itm_ora.historical_class_code,'-1', DECODE (itm_ora.current_class_code,'1','A','2','I','4','O','6','N','-1'),itm_ora.historical_class_code))
